supply, and learned that gravity supplies

176
00:11:54,140 --> 00:11:58,399
in hilly areas are usually simple systems
which do not require high degree of maintenance.

177
00:11:58,399 --> 00:12:03,300
Furthermore, we looked at the basic operating
principles and differences of various common

178
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:08,850
types of pumps such as impulse pumps, positive
displacement pumps and velocity pumps and

179
00:12:08,850 --> 00:12:12,150
learned how to read pump curves of centrifugal
pumps.

180
